<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧看着这群强盗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他浑身发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抱......抱歉！”他说，“但是......</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们只不过是两个和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们一点儿钱都没有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就有什么就给什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个强盗说着走近了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求求你们！”唐僧说，“我们......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抬起了手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来处理这些强盗吧！师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走向这群强盗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看这只小猴子！”其中一人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空也大笑起来：“是，我是只猴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的个头很小，这是事实。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从耳朵里取出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，你们应该还是怕我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的金箍棒一直变大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼睛里闪烁着怒火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那猴子是个妖怪！”一个男人大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快跑！”另一个男人叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这群强盗一个绊倒一个，拼命想要逃走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空举起金箍棒，准备朝他们砸下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“住手，悟空！”唐僧高叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要伤害他们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空转过身来，那群人飞快地跑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？”悟空问，“他们要害我们啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“佛家以慈悲为怀，从不伤人。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我宁愿自己受伤，也不愿伤到他人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑：“简直太可笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们就应该打他们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧摇摇头：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你太残忍，太暴力了，悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空生气了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我刚刚救了你的命！”他大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么能责怪我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空停了一下又说：“我无法接受。我走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳上空中不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧叹了口气，继续赶路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来，他看到了一个老妇人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“高僧。”那妇人说，“你要去哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去西天。”唐僧回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有人和你一起去吗？”妇人问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一个人没法去那里的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我曾有一个同伴。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为他的暴力行为，我责怪了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他就生气走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的同伴会回来的。”那妇人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他回来的时候，骗他戴上这个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从袋子里拿出了一个金属做的头箍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要他行为不当，你就念这紧箍咒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那老妇人悄悄地把口诀告诉了唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您！”唐僧说，“但您怎么会... ...”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时一道光闪过，那妇人升到了空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨！”唐僧叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他赶紧从马上下来行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>此时，悟空正坐在东海龙宫里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和龙王正在喝茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望你能从所受的惩罚中吸取教训。”龙王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有啊，我有吸取教训啊。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会再给玉帝惹麻烦了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王喝了一口茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你现在做什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我本来是陪一个和尚去西天取经。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我向观音菩萨保证的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那很不错啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空耸耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是不错，但我现在不干了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王放下了茶杯：“为什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那和尚态度不好。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他对我大喊大叫。他说我又残忍又暴力。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王紧张地咳起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，悟空。那和尚说的也不是不对。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空瞪着龙王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你什么意思？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王犹豫了一下说道：“你有时候确实很暴力。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空双臂交叉看着地面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王继续说：“不仅如此，你已经向观音菩萨保证了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>352234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空，也许你才是那个态度不好的人？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>